AUTHOR: RAMESH BASUKALA <basukalarameshATgmailDOTcom>
DATE: 02.18.2014 
This script queries the vcenter server and send report on email with following properties:
  - Name
  - VM Status
  - Producation Status
  - Primary Sysadmin
  - OS
  - Memory (MB)
  - #CPU
  - VM Version
  - VM Tool Status
  - VMX
  - Network
  - Disks
  - Snapshots
  - Notes

VMWare Tools must be running on VM for this script to work.

USAGE: 
     $python <scriptname> [vmhost_list_file] 
        Default: vmhost_list_file: vms.txt

     $python getVMStats.py myhosts.txt
 
